snippet: Yorkshire clinched its first title in 13 years after demolishing Nottinghamshire by an innings and 152 runs at Trent Bridge.
abstract: Yorkshire defeats Nottinghamshire, clinching its first English County Championship cricket title in 13 years.
lead_paragraph: Yorkshire clinched its first title in 13 years after demolishing Nottinghamshire by an innings and 152 runs at Trent Bridge.

headline.main: Yorkshire Grabs English County Championship Title
